{"id": "7564", "post": "<div class=\"post-7564 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-epidrive-com tag-exclusive tag-openvz tag-phoenix tag-usa\" id=\"post-7564\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/epidrive-4-95month-1gb-or-6-95month-2gb-openvz-vps-in-phoenix-arizona/\" rel=\"bookmark\">EpiDrive \u2013 $4.95/month 1GB or $6.95/month 2GB OpenVZ VPS in Phoenix, Arizona</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/epidrive-com/\" rel=\"tag\">epidrive.com</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/exclusive/\" rel=\"tag\">exclusive</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/openvz/\" rel=\"tag\">openvz</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/phoenix/\" rel=\"tag\">phoenix</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/usa/\" rel=\"tag\">USA</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> August 29, 2015 @ 1:00 am, by Jonathan Tan</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"https://www.epidrive.com/\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIzMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTg4IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMzAwIDE4OCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/EpiDrive-Premium_Quality_Hosting_Made_Affordable_-_Epidrive_Webhosting_Solutions_-_2014-09-15_10.53.00-300x188.png.webp\" alt=\"EpiDrive-Premium_Quality_Hosting_Made_Affordable_-_Epidrive_Webhosting_Solutions_-_2014-09-15_10.53.00\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\"></a></p><p>Bryson, from <a href=\"https://www.epidrive.com/\">EpiDrive</a>, has sent us two exclusive offers to celebrate their anniversary with the LowEndBox community. They lowered the price from their <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/epidrive-5-95month-1gb-openvz-vps-in-phoenix-arizona/\">last feature</a> to give our readers a treat. A big congratulations to EpiDrive for this milestone!</p><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>EDVS Level 1</strong><p></p><ul><li>2 CPU cores</li><li>1GB RAM</li><li>1GB vSwap</li><li>30GB HDD space</li><li>250GB traffic</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>2x IPv6</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>$4.95/month (Coupon: <strong><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'lucida grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.020000457763672px;\">EDLEB1024M</span></strong>)</li><li><a href=\"https://www.epidrive.com/clients/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=7\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td><strong>EDVS Level 2</strong><p></p><ul><li>3 CPU cores</li><li>2GB RAM</li><li>2GB vSwap</li><li>60GB HDD space</li><li>500GB traffic</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>2x IPv4</li><li>5x IPv6</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>$6.95/month (Coupon: <strong><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'lucida grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20.020000457763672px;\">EDLEB2048M</span></strong>)</li><li><a href=\"https://www.epidrive.com/clients/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=8\">Order here</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Bryson is no stranger to LowEndBox. He was the previous owner of fraphost.com, which was sold when he became busy at the time. He started EpiDrive about a year ago with a long term vision in mind. Their anniversary is a good indicator that EpiDrive is doing something good. Host nodes for this offer have Intel Xeon E3 (1240v2 and 1240v3) and hardware RAID1 disk configuration. We highly encourage our readers to share their thoughts on the comments section below.</p><p><span id=\"more-7564\"></span></p><p>EpiDrive supports payment method using Paypal and Credit/Debit cards and they provide 99% uptime guarantee. Additional IPv4 addresses are priced at $3.95/month, though they are $2.50/month if you buy 5 at a time. Their servers are TUN/TAP and PPP enabled. Spam/Bulk Mail, Warez, and CPU intensive scripts are not allowed. Kindly read their <a href=\"https://www.epidrive.com/terms.html\">Terms of Service</a> and <a href=\"https://www.epidrive.com/privacy.html\">Privacy Policy</a> before making any purchase.</p><p><strong>Network information</strong></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">PhoenixNAP \u2013 Phoenix, AZ, USA</span><br>\nTest IPv4: 107.158.239.251<br>\nTest file: <a href=\"http://107.158.239.251/testfile\">http://107.158.239.251/testfile</a></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fepidrive-4-95month-1gb-or-6-95month-2gb-openvz-vps-in-phoenix-arizona%2F&amp;t=EpiDrive%20%E2%80%93%20%244.95%2Fmonth%201GB%20or%20%246.95%2Fmonth%202GB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20Arizona\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=EpiDrive%20%E2%80%93%20%244.95%2Fmonth%201GB%20or%20%246.95%2Fmonth%202GB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20Arizona&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fepidrive-4-95month-1gb-or-6-95month-2gb-openvz-vps-in-phoenix-arizona%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-ne